channel.title: Ekstrak - Logo Evolution [1 Year SoundCloud Anniversary]
channel.description:
It’s been a year since I existed on SoundCloud. Thanks for the support everyone. I decided to do an evolution of my logos— from April 2017 to April 2018.
(Keep in mind that there is a lot of em. Get some popcorn if you want to.)
